Package: ghosts
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.9), python3-curses
Recommends: tmux
Description: Terminal scene viewer with animated effects
 Ghosts renders 9 animated scenes in 24-bit colour mapped to xterm-256,
 built on a notcurses-inspired plane and compositor model.
 .
 Scenes include: Ghost (terminal content drift with trail modes), Matrix
 Rain, Rain Drops, Plasma, Topo Flyover, Glitch Screen, Bio Scan,
 Computer Sim, and the interactive Shadytel Switchboard with PANIC mode.
 .
 Pure Python — no external dependencies beyond the standard library.
 Runs inside tmux to capture live terminal content for the Ghost scene.
